1. Go to https://trello.com/app-key/ and get api_key
2. On the same page click "Genereate Token manualy"
3. use API_KEY and TOKEN as header in requests:
Authorization: OAuth oauth_consumer_key="{{API_KEY}}", oauth_token="{{TOKEN}}"

4. Use API documentation to create api requests:
https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/trello/rest/api-group-actions/

Useful links
https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/trello/
https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/trello/guides/rest-api/api-introduction/
https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/trello/guides/rest-api/authorization/
https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/trello/guides/rest-api/rate-limits/
